        "id": 1177549
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-04-07T14:07:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah, I\u0027m going with what\u0027s convenient right now, but let\u0027s refactor this out for bitwise reuse at need?",
      "parentUuid": "6878cb01_f96cb350",
